item.title: Can someone please help me with this issue?
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

runescape sucks:

This error just means that the version of java you’re using to try and run the .class files is lower than the one it was compiled in.

This.

Download the latest JDK (It will install the latest JRE as well) from here. Then, go into your control panel and remove your old java versions (Anything under version 1.8.0_45). If you set your environmental variables to your computer, go in and update them with your new version.

Now, after that’s all said and done, run the server again.
